Sample n things out if 1:maxValue with replacement

Sample from 1:maxValue vector without creating it, using runif

sample_large(n, maxValue, seed)

Arguments

n

Number of samples expected
maxValue

Length of the vector to sample from
seed

Value of seed

Value

An numeric vector, with replacement sample of 1:maxValue

Examples

as.character(try(sample(1:1e20, 100), silent = TRUE))
#> [1] "Error in 1:1e+20 : result would be too long a vector\n"
sample_large(100, 1e20)
